commit.message: Update with number of words in the dictionary.
Updated with permission from "Navnegruppen" from Dansk Ornitologisk Forening
Updated with "Navnegruppen" from Dansk Ornitologisk Forening

Updated with 4853 new words that are all bird names. These names
are the work of "Navnegruppen" in Dansk Ornitologisk Forening and
used with their permission.
Account of permissions from major third party contributors.
Updated with some major thord party contributors

Reintroduced the period sign as allowed in the middle and end of
words.

Huge update with more than a million new words, including some
proper nouns. Many of these words are old Danish words that have
gone out of use. But they should included in a word database that aims
to be as complete as at all possible.
Aligned version to that of DSDO - 3.2

New version, 3.2. Based on cleaned up DSDO word list. Added some new
words. Aligned GPL versions between aspell-da and DSDO to GPLv2.
Modified some copyright information. Adjusted da.dat. Removed compiled
and compressed versions of word list. Now include only the raw word list.
